<div class="event-time"><span class="time"><strong>Local: </strong>Online(Virtual)</span><span class="price"><strong>R$1300,00( Até 12X no Cartão)</strong></span> <a class="btn-book" href="https://pagseguro.uol.com.br/checkout/v2/payment.html?code=5CA51E2C37378A1FF47EDF85C8778040" target="_blank" title="Book now">Matricular</a></div>
<div class="event-author">
